metadata.name: ControlNet Ape #1
metadata.description: Step into our world where art meets advanced technology. Our 555 Ethereum NFTs showcase unique renditions of Apes, crafted with a new diffusion method called ControlNet. Our artist, inspired by Roy Lichtenstein, prompts an engaging discourse on contemporary society. Each masterpiece is an embodiment of counter-culture, with bold colors and intricate details. This groundbreaking collection is a must-have for those seeking to express individuality and a sense of defiance.
